data.description: Great self sufficient, AFFORDABLE, ranchette WITH WATER RIGHTS irrigating 16 acres of the 20 acre parcel.  Five shares of the Monte Vista Canal service the pivot system that waters the hayfield.  There is a ditch that goes through the east side of the property, and the Rio Grande Canal that is on the west side of the property.   This property is perfect for the family who wants to live more independantly.  The main house has a spacious 3529 square feet of living space including a family room, living room, spacious kitchen with new and almost new appliances, seperate dining room, four bedrooms on the main floor including a master with a full bathroom, and two guest bedrooms on the main floor with a 3/4 bathroom.  Upstairs are two more bedrooms and another 3/4 bathroom.  There is also a large sunroom on the main level with hookups for a hot tub.  The home is completely self sufficient with a large solar system and the 20 +/- acres has historically grown alfalfa and alfalfa grass mixed hay.  There are also numerous outbuildings that include storage buildings, horse barn, chicken coop, and a spacious 20 x 20' greenhouse.  In addition there is an excellent 15 gpm well that services the home and lawn, garden, fire protection, and watering of livestock.  Ready to add your taste to the home and make it your own!  Short drive to all conveniences!
